item.title: By: Rosie Skiles
item.dc:creator: Rosie Skiles
item.description: On April 20 I sent a number of email Easter greeting cards. I know you sent them but I have not heard back from some of those people. I know you cannot guarantee that. i was wondering in you just delete them or do you keep them in your pending file? I would like you to delete all that have not replied. Thank you.
